{"user":"y8opEFHvV7c7QIhq","type":0,"content":"<div class=\"dnd5e chat-card item-card\" data-actor-id=\"I4EU9sR5qy78aWKc\" data-item-id=\"qMfGeZtLOMY76zkU\">\n    <header class=\"card-header flexrow\">\n        <img src=\"icons/magic/life/heart-glowing-red.webp\" title=\"Second Wind\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" />\n        <h3 class=\"item-name\">Second Wind</h3>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"card-content\">\n        Once per short rest, you can use a bonus action to regain 1d10 + <a class=\"inline-roll inline-result\" data-tooltip=\"5\" data-roll=\"%7B%22class%22%3A%22Roll%22%2C%22options%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22dice%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22formula%22%3A%22%20+%205%22%2C%22terms%22%3A%5B%7B%22class%22%3A%22NumericTerm%22%2C%22options%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22evaluated%22%3Atrue%2C%22number%22%3A5%7D%5D%2C%22total%22%3A5%2C%22evaluated%22%3Atrue%7D\"><i class=\"fas fa-dice-d20\"></i>5</a> HP.\n<details>\n  <summary>\n    More Details\n  </summary>\n  <p>\n    </p><p>You have a limited well of stamina that you can draw on to protect yourself from harm. On your turn, you can use a bonus action to regain hit points equal to 1d10 + your fighter level. Once you use this feature, you must finish a short or long rest before you can use it again.</p>\n  <p></p>\n</details>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card-buttons\">\n        \n\n        <button data-action=\"damage\">\n            Heilung\n            \n        </button>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    </div>\n\n    <footer class=\"card-footer\">\n        <span>1 Bonusaktion</span>\n        <span>Selbst</span>\n        <span>Selbst</span>\n    </footer>\n</div>","flavor":"Second Wind","speaker":{"scene":"SSWWGKvqtyDQf1CK","token":"FSpp1Yy50aag68bv","actor":"I4EU9sR5qy78aWKc","alias":"Barogart"},"flags":{"core":{"canPopout":true},"dnd5e":{"use":{"type":"feat","itemId":"qMfGeZtLOMY76zkU","itemUuid":"Actor.I4EU9sR5qy78aWKc.Item.qMfGeZtLOMY76zkU"}}},"whisper":[],"blind":false,"timestamp":1695502535927,"rolls":[],"sound":null,"emote":false,"_id":"AVaww4dkAmQRKL0O"}
